[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     15[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     16[0m:[38;5;10m[49m The recipe has no CRITICAL findings and 2 HIGH findings. Both are addressable with targeted additions. The architecture is sound for the stated scale, HIPAA considerations are well-handled in the Prerequisites table, and the domain treatment is clinically accurate. The equity audit discussion and explainability emphasis are particular strengths.
